/f extension download <Extension> - Downloads extension
/f extension list - Displays the currently installed extensions & their versions
/f extension refresh - Reloads the extension list from github to get the newest extension available
/f extension remove - Removes the extension (sometimes). The best way to remove them is to stop the server, go to /plugins/ImprovedFactions/Extensions/ and delete the extension .jar

tobero: 
Pinned a message.
tobero: 
```If you have encountered a bug, please follow these steps```

As it would get the bug fixed faster, please make an issue on github, using this link:
https://github.com/ToberoCat/ImprovedFactions_new/issues/new?assignees=&labels=bug&template=bug_report.md&title=%5BBug%5D+Quick+and+useful+description

**How to do it:**

- First, you need to have a github account to report a bug
- After you have done that, please fill out the form you get filled on github automatically.
- Set the title to: [Bug] Describe Your Problem

This I need (If they make sense for your crash):
- The error message / entire console log
- How I can reproduce it and test if I fixed it
- What should have happened (Only if it's not a crash)
- The version of the plugin & the version of your server

Things that make my file easier:
- Include screenshots, if it's something visual / hard to explain
- You can always reformat the layout as long as it includes the required things I need
